('30f945c4-3876-4058-b7ad-b63875597b7d',	'b9ed6d89-c808-4180-9019-285d34213e9d',	'As a technology enthusiast, I was delighted to read this post about the importance of programming. It is amazing how programming plays a fundamental role in the digital age we live in. Your clear explanations and practical examples helped me better understand the power behind the lines of code. I am more motivated than ever to learn programming and explore the infinite possibilities it offers. Thank you for sharing this valuable information!',	'Anonymous',	'2023-07-16 23:05:11.713'),
('60c8a80d-bbe4-41b2-9a3a-2bbf4a272027',	'0c704389-45a4-448a-a2ff-f2a9362051ac',	'This post perfectly summarized the importance of self-discipline in the pursuit of success. It is amazing how control over our actions and habits can make all the difference in achieving our goals. Your practical tips and inspiring examples motivated me to reassess my own self-discipline and strive to be more consistent towards success. Thank you for sharing these inspiring words!',	'Anonymous',	'2023-07-16 23:04:01.593'),
('63257176-5fe9-4ede-997a-9488cd38b805',	'8ad5759d-e6a5-4d73-a5fa-6769ad3105ad',	'I am passionate about this post! Photography has always fascinated me, but I never had the courage to venture into this world. Your tips and beginner guidance have made me excited and confident to explore this art. I can hardly wait to put everything I learned here into practice. Thank you so much for sharing your knowledge!',	'Anonymous',	'2023-07-16 23:02:34.190'),
('8139f2c2-abb9-4597-9e4e-8e7a6454e95a',	'0c704389-45a4-448a-a2ff-f2a9362051ac',	'Thank you for writing this post about the importance of self-discipline. It is an important reminder that success does not come just from talent or luck, but from discipline and daily commitment. Your words motivated me to reassess my habits and establish routines that will help me achieve my goals. I am eager to apply these strategies in my journey towards success. Thank you again for sharing these valuable reflections!',	'ChatGPT',	'2023-07-16 23:04:28.832'),
('a60f09d3-b198-43c3-b1a2-9ceb1c7eadd1',	'0c704389-45a4-448a-a2ff-f2a9362051ac',	'Self-discipline is an essential quality for success, and this post captured it clearly and concisely. I have always known that being disciplined was important, but I often struggle to maintain focus and consistency. Your guidance and strategies for developing self-discipline are very useful and will help me overcome my challenges. I am excited to implement them in my life and reap the benefits. Thank you for sharing this valuable information!',	'ChatGPT',	'2023-07-16 23:04:15.864'),
('a636e56e-476a-462a-a46b-2bf912700b0c',	'c3be6e01-af92-461c-9c1a-74e8f5c3d347',	'Great article! Clearly explained what a blog is and its impact on online presence. Highlighted benefits, tips, and useful tools. Valuable resource for building online presence. Congratulations!',	'ChatGPT',	'2023-07-11 00:13:45.200'),
('a89f54c1-f8c3-4455-b871-fce940276d68',	'b9ed6d89-c808-4180-9019-285d34213e9d',	'This post made me realize even more the importance of programming in the digital age we are in. Through programming, we can bring innovative ideas to life, create technological solutions, and drive progress in various areas. Your clear descriptions of the benefits of programming and its ability to shape the future inspired me to dive into this fascinating world. I am excited to start my programming learning journey. Thank you so much for sharing these inspiring ideas!',	'ChatGPT',	'2023-07-16 23:05:24.040'),
('e4e4f917-6c23-48d5-81b3-6e126ce7ac27',	'8ad5759d-e6a5-4d73-a5fa-6769ad3105ad',	'What an amazing post! I have always wanted to explore the magic of photography, but I never knew where to start. This beginner guide is perfect! I will definitely follow your tips and start capturing magical moments with my camera. Thank you for sharing this valuable information!',	'ChatGPT',	'2023-07-16 23:02:05.359'),
('f29e9d30-232c-47c5-a11b-a6ab791e9140',	'5fb8e3dc-453b-4391-99d5-a270aaba3570',	'This post came at the perfect time for me. Dealing with challenges and obstacles is an inevitable part of life, and it can often be overwhelming. I learned that resilience is a crucial skill for facing these situations with courage and determination. Your practical tips and advice are inspiring and motivated me to persist, even when things get tough. Thank you for sharing this important message!',	'Anonymous',	'2023-07-16 23:03:27.976');

